					sit illo neque rem omnis quaerat, nam similique vitae delectus ad magni vel quo maxime, magnam placeat.
					Reprehenderit, distinctio aliquam?</p>
				  <a href="/blog/my-first-article/" class="btn btn--primary">Continue Reading</a>
				</article>
			  </li>
			  <li>
				<article class="snippet">
				  <img src="/assets/blog/article-2.jpg" alt="This is a test" class="snippet__image">
				  <h3 class="snippet__title"><a href="/blog/my-second-article/">My Second Article</a></h3>
				  <p class="snippet__meta">by <span>Kevin Powell</span> on <span>May 14, 2021</span></p>
